title: China aces test of next-gen lunar capsule and rocket in effort to land humans on moon before NASA (video)
description: China just took another step toward landing astronauts on the moon, acing a key abort test with its Mengzhou crew capsule and pulling off a soft splashdown with the returning rocket.
